text: Coming 2 America is an American comedy movie. It is a sequel to Coming to America (1988). The movie is directed by Craig Brewer, from a screenplay by David Sheffield, Barry W. Blaustein, and Kenya Barris. It is based on characters created by Eddie Murphy. The movie stars Eddie Murphy, Arsenio Hall, Jermaine Fowler, Leslie Jones, Shari Headley, John Amos, Lawal Olatubosun, Wesley Snipes, and James Earl Jones. The movie is was released in December 2020 in the United States. ==References== Category:2021 comedy movies Category:Sequel movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Movies about royalty Category:Movies set in a fictional country Category:Movies set in Africa Category:Movies directed by Craig Brewer Category:Movies about families
